{
  "texts": [
    "Researchers started to demonstrate stronger interest in this topic in 2007 with constant growth resulting in 19 articles in 2022, which is the highest number of articles per year on the topic of dynamic pricing in e-commerce.",
    "There are 61% of articles (94 articles) and 37% of proceedings papers (57 documents).",
    "The rest represents 2% of early access documents (4 papers) and 4 reviews (2%).",
    "Some articles are of two document types, namely article and early access article.",
    "As the majority of the documents are scientific articles, the sources or publication titles are scientific journals."
  ]
}